r this fall. If you are interested in following the development of WordPress and WordPress related applications, here is a list:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href="http://wpdevel.wordpress.com/" title="WordPress Development Updates">WordPress Development Updates Blog</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://twitter.com/wpdevel" title="Twitter / wpdevel">WPDevel Twitter</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://trac.wordpress.org/timeline" title="WordPress Development Trac Timeline">WordPress Development Trac Timeline</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://iphone.trac.wordpress.org/timeline" title="WordPress iPhone App">WordPress iPhone App Trac Timeline</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://trac.wordpress.org/roadmap" title="WordPress roadmap">WordPress Roadmap</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://www.blogherald.com/tag/wordpress-wednesday-news/" title="WordPress Wednesday News">Blog Herald WordPress Wednesday News</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src="http://lorelle.files.wordpress.com/2006/08/sig.gif" alt="" /><br />\n<hr />\n<p><font size="-1"><b>Site Search Tags:</b> <a href="http://lorelle.wordpress.com/index.php?s=wordpress" rel="tag">wordpress</a>, <a href="http://lorelle.wordpress.com/index.php?s=wordpress+news" rel="tag">wordpress news</a>, <a href="http://lorelle.wordpress.com/index.php?s=wordpress+versions" rel="tag">wordpress versions</a>, <a href="http://lorelle.wordpress.com/index.php?s=wordpress+upgrade" rel="tag">wordpress upgrade</a>, <a href="http://lorelle.wordpress.com/index.php?s=wordpress+update" rel="tag">wordpress update</a>, <a href="http://lorelle.wordpress.com/index.php?s=wordpress+2.6" rel="tag">wordpress 2.6</a>, <a href="http://lorelle.wordpress.com/index.php?s=wordpress+2.6.2" rel="tag">wordpress 2.6.2</a>, <a href="http://lorelle.wordpress.com/index.php?s=security" rel="tag">security</a>, <a href="http://lorelle.wordpress.com/index.php?s=security+update" rel="tag">security update</a>, <a href="http://lorelle.wordpress.com/index.php?s=mandatory+update" rel="tag">mandatory update</a>, <a href="http://